divs: Sighting DetailsStanding outside in the front of the house saying goodbye to a friend and noticed 2 objects overhead.......if stars are the size of a dime these were the size of a quarter.......they flew very fast and disappeared over the horizon.........they were kind of triangular in shape and had a milky white light around them.
Summary: 2 objects one ahead of the other flew overhead very fast and disappeared over the horizon
